    <item>
      <title>PoshC2: Sharp_v4_x64.dll</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/bubka/investigations/poschc2-sharp_v4_x64.dll/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Nov 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/bubka/investigations/poschc2-sharp_v4_x64.dll/</guid>
      <description>A .NET DLL decodes architecture-specific shellcode from an embedded base64 string, allocates executable memory, and spawns a thread to execute it. The shellcode performs NTDLL unhooking, AMSI and ETW patching before executing an embedded PE payload identified as a PoshC2 dropper.</description>
      
